{"tid":596481,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"GrayKey強制解鎖iPhone","createTime":"2018-03-17T16:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T03:40:52.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ece5de6ee5bf2baa5001122b578ac7ab3ec2610c","tid":596481,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"Grayshift 推出的解鎖 iPhone 裝置「GrayKey」。機器本身還算輕巧，附帶兩條 Lightning 線，可以一次破解兩部 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/1521207844-24ac0241a88ca3d68130aa8451ba316a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F1521207844-24ac0241a88ca3d68130aa8451ba316a.png&h=4338826d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 GrayKey 連接 iPhone 後，會在短短兩分鐘內取得系統權限，並安裝一套破解密碼的軟體，若使用者的密碼為四位數字，大概幾個小時即可破解；若密碼為六位數以上，則需要耗費幾天。<br />\n<br />\n當 GrayKey 破解 iPhone 後，所有裝置裡的資料就會被下載至 GrayKey 內，此時就可讀取裡面的照片、鑰匙串等資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/1521207845-2f2cab8dc9b29d0d54c52af5809badeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-amod9fa3ka.zi.org.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F1521207845-2f2cab8dc9b29d0d54c52af5809badeb.png&h=06986226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前尚不清楚 GrayKey 販售的對象是誰，很有可能僅限美國的執法機關使用。GrayKey 的價格相較於先前 Cellebrite 的方案便宜不少。據悉 GrayKey 有兩個版本，一款為僅能使用 300 次，且需連接網路，售價 15,000 美元（約 11萬5千港元），超過使用次數後每次破解要價 500 美元；而不限次數的版本則要價 30,000 美元（約 23萬港元）。"},{"pid":"800325d4aaba2329c582c47bb222b4a225028fcd","tid":596481,"uid":25612,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"Apple自己買返黎研究極速封左個漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班俾左錢嘅仆街就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c730dc7e822b57a510082d4dd50c2a4381b94a92","tid":596481,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d8ba5634ca96e2c530ec9a74d02c5c5d8c5570","tid":596481,"uid":113059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"上次要等幾十年個大陸女人有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630d205ad585660fefcc672d7649da00733f5ca5","tid":596481,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25d8ba5634ca96e2c530ec9a74d02c5c5d8c5570","tid":596481,"uid":113059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"上次要等幾十年個大陸女人有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"嗰條友第二日搞掂左用得返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  bug中bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1a6465c0d2653c3a88f5ccdcb2715e77e183b8","tid":596481,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}